國不是法治國家，是人治國家！」畫面曝光震撼網友。<br />\n<br />\nYouTube頻道「舊視頻（影片）備份」今年5月12日上傳1段2005年的「中國執行死刑槍決現場」紀錄片（<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5L-H2V7m8vc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5L-H2V7m8vc&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0qVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=6dc28d46\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5L-H2V7m8vc</a>），在行刑日當天對1名中國女死囚進行專訪，她因殺害丈夫被法官判處死刑，鏡頭前她看似有苦難言，但認為自己沒什麼好說的了，坦然接受處決，但也擔心年幼的孩子該怎麼辦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhOixOO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhOixOO.jpg&h=585cb91d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國女死囚（圖中）臨刑前，對著鏡頭說：「想聽實話嗎？中國不是法治國家，是人治國家！」（圖取自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女死囚接著被帶去確認罪名，以及查核是否符合中國法定流程，確認無誤後，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:50:38.000Z","msg":"諗起零零漆"},{"pid":"f08f14ddc1c713244ce61a482e335e8ec6b4ebab","tid":2060674,"uid":125364,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"人之將死 其言也善"},{"pid":"d0e6863f47f06d44c707797d5de7a87c967a5c83","tid":2060674,"uid":71433,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"35c39a55edcd72094fa8f7bc256d1b0d823d07a9","tid":2060674,"uid":121197,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T00:32:29.000Z","msg":"如果佢有睇國產凌凌漆袋定張100蚊的話..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:52:46.000Z","msg":"好似係50"},{"pid":"e3afcdfd988f85961810d6b53d80d97f5fa7654d","tid":2060674,"uid":192517,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b9f9bd3e10477003859d92c47c9a77edfdc761d3","tid":2060674,"uid":49588,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T00:12:55.000Z","msg":"聯合國入面居然有一個極邪惡的惡魔國家做常任理事國，世界人民都不好過。<br />\n<br />\n那種滲透，用錢收買，打輿論戰<br />\n<br />\n真的不能睇少"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:56:09.000Z","msg":"以前啲文明國仲要養住佢<br />\n宜家肯醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c